1363
01:55:21,320 --> 01:55:24,630
<i># Now my hand's on the wheel</i>

1364
01:55:24,760 --> 01:55:27,479
<i># Of somethin' that's real</i>

1365
01:55:28,080 --> 01:55:29,718
<i># And I feel</i>

